Typedef Documentation

typedef OsclBasicDateTimeStruct __Validate__BasicTimeDateStruct__

OsclBasicDateTimeStruct type should be defined to the platform-specific date + time type.

typedef OsclBasicTimeStruct __Validate__BasicTimeStruct__

OSCL_HAS_UNIX_TIME_FUNCS macro should be set to 1 if the target platform supports unix time of day functions. Otherwise it should be set to 0. OsclBasicTimeStruct type should be defined to the platform-specific time of day type.
